                        <br/><br/><br/><h2>文 献</h2><br><ol><br><li id="R1"><span class='au'>Dyson, H. J. & Wright, P. E.</span>: <span class="ti">Intrinsically unstructured proteins and their functions.</span> <span class='so'>Nat. Rev. Mol. Cell Biol., 6, 197-208 (2005)[<a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/15738986" target="_blank">PubMed</a>]</span></li><br><li id="R2"><span class='au'>Banani, S. F., Lee, H. O., Hyman, A. A. et al.</span>: <span class="ti">Biomolecular condensates: organizers of cellular biochemistry.</span> <span class='so'>Nat. Rev. Mol. Cell Biol., 18, 285-298 (2017)[<a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/28225081" target="_blank">PubMed</a>]</span></li><br><li id="R3"><span class='au'>Taylor, J. P., Brown, R. H. Jr. & Cleveland, D. W.</span>: <span class="ti">Decoding ALS: from genes to mechanism.</span> <span class='so'>Nature, 539, 197-206 (2016)[<a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/27830784" target="_blank">PubMed</a>]</span></li><br><li id="R4"><span class='au'>Kato, M., Han, T. W., Xie, S. et al.</span>: <span class="ti">Cell-free formation of RNA granules: low complexity sequence domains form dynamic fibers within hydrogels.</span> <span class='so'>Cell, 149, 753-767 (2012)[<a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/22579281" target="_blank">PubMed</a>] [<a href="http://first.lifesciencedb.jp/archives/4969" target="_blank">新着論文レビュー</a>]</span></li><br><li id="R5"><span class='au'>Lin, Y., Mori, E., Kato, M. et al.</span>: <span class="ti">Toxic PR poly-dipeptides encoded by the C9orf72 repeat expansion target LC domain polymers.</span> <span class='so'>Cell, 167, 789-802.e12 (2016)[<a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/27768897" target="_blank">PubMed</a>] [<a href="http://first.lifesciencedb.jp/archives/14807" target="_blank">新着論文レビュー</a>]</span></li><br><li id="R6"><span class='au'>Xiang, S., Kato, M., Wu, L. C. et al.</span>: <span class="ti">The LC domain of hnRNPA2 adopts similar conformations in hydrogel p